      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are honored to present this vehicle, an exemplar of automotive preservation maintained to an exacting standard. This unit remains in pristine condition, offering a showroom-grade aesthetic and mechanical integrity that distinguishes it from standard market offerings. Every detail has been meticulously curated to ensure an ownership experience indistinguishable from a new acquisition. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to secure an investment-grade asset of unparalleled quality.",
